{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a refined, luxury-brand section titled “What We Stand For.”
    The design should express timeless elegance and quiet confidence.
    Display four core values — Authenticity, Curation, Hospitality, and Sustainability — each represented with a minimalist gold-line icon and short description in elegant typography.
    
    The layout must feel balanced and airy, with soft cream or ivory background and generous spacing.
    On desktop, arrange the four pillars horizontally in equal columns beneath the title and a delicate italic tagline:
    “Our idea is to let you feel the joy of wearing clothes & passing them on.”
    On mobile, stack them vertically with smooth breathing space between icons and text for an editorial flow.
    
    The aesthetic should evoke high-end fashion branding — think quiet luxury, subtle gold tones, refined serif headings, and modern sans-serif body text.
    No harsh shadows or strong borders — only softness, precision, and grace., section should have the ability to add image for every Value inn Icon place to replace icon with image we made
{% enddoc %}
